Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phase Two Tester",
  "email": "tester@noorlocator.local",
  "password": "Tester123!Pass"
}

###

GET {{NoorLocator.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Accept: application/json
